INSERT INTO rentalContracts (vehicleId, clientId, contractId, rentalStartDate, rentalEndDate, dailyRate, totalAmount, discount, finalAmount, status, pickupKm, fuelLevel, createdAt)
SELECT v.id, c.id, 'CTR-TEST-001', '2026-02-01', '2026-02-03', 40, 80, 0, 80, 'active', 14000, 'Full', NOW()
FROM vehicles v, clients c
WHERE v.plateNumber = 'M 412458' AND c.id = (SELECT MIN(id) FROM clients)
LIMIT 1;
